description: Thousands accused PM Janez Jansa of using the coronavirus crisis as a pretext to restrict freedoms.
title: Slovenia cyclists hold anti-government protest
title_page: Slovenia cyclists hold anti-government protest - BBC News
maintext: For the most part, it was a calm and good-natured affair, our correspondent adds. But the riders did chant slogans against the prime minister, including "thieves" and "down with the government".
